          <h3 style="font-size: 1.15em; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 15px;">AI and IoT Integration</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>AI algorithms optimize elevator movement, traffic patterns, and maintenance schedules, reducing wait times and energy use.</li>
            <li>IoT sensors enable real-time monitoring, remote troubleshooting, and data-driven service contracts, minimizing breakdowns and enhancing reliability—especially critical in high-rise buildings.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 style="font-size: 1.15em; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 15px;">Touchless, User-Friendly Controls</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Touchless interfaces, voice commands, and mobile apps reduce contact, offering greater hygiene—a must-have in post-pandemic architectural planning.</li>
            <li>Gesture-based controls and accessibility features aid senior citizens and differently-abled users, aligning with updated Indian Building Codes and BIS standards.</li>
            </ul>

          <h3 style="font-size: 1.15em; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 15px;">Sustainability and Energy Efficiency</h3>
